Function Menu
Begin
	Clear
	Color cyan
	PrintLine "Welcome to Math Practice!"
	Color none
	PrintLine "Press 1 for addition practice."
	PrintLine "Press 2 for multiplication practice."
	PrintLine "Press 3 to exit."

	Var x
	Input x

	If x Equals 1
		Call AddPractice
	Else x Equals 2
		Call MpPractice
	Else x Equals 3
		Exit
	Else
		Color red
		PrintLine "Unknown input"
		Color none
		Exit
	Stop
End

Call Menu
